📦 Add / Remove Elements

| Method         | Mutates? | Purpose                          |
| -------------- | -------- | -------------------------------- |
| `push()`       | ✅        | Add to end                       |
| `pop()`        | ✅        | Remove from end                  |
| `shift()`      | ✅        | Remove from start                |
| `unshift()`    | ✅        | Add to start                     |
| `splice()`     | ✅        | Insert/remove anywhere           |
| `fill()`       | ✅        | Fill array with value            |
| `copyWithin()` | ✅        | Copy part of array within itself |


🔍 Search / Find

| Method            | Mutates? | Returns                |
| ----------------- | -------- | ---------------------- |
| `includes()`      | ❌        | true/false             |
| `indexOf()`       | ❌        | First index            |
| `lastIndexOf()`   | ❌        | Last index             |
| `find()`          | ❌        | First matching element |
| `findIndex()`     | ❌        | Index of first match   |
| `findLast()`      | ❌        | Last matching element  |
| `findLastIndex()` | ❌        | Index of last match    |


🔄 Transform Arrays

| Method         | Mutates? | Purpose                |
| -------------- | -------- | ---------------------- |
| `map()`        | ❌        | Transform elements     |
| `filter()`     | ❌        | Keep matching elements |
| `flat()`       | ❌        | Flatten nested arrays  |
| `flatMap()`    | ❌        | Map + Flatten          |
| `concat()`     | ❌        | Merge arrays           |
| `slice()`      | ❌        | Copy portion           |
| `toSpliced()`  | ❌        | Non-mutating splice    |
| `toSorted()`   | ❌        | Non-mutating sort      |
| `toReversed()` | ❌        | Non-mutating reverse   |


🧮 Aggregate / Calculate

| Method          | Mutates? | Purpose                |
| --------------- | -------- | ---------------------- |
| `reduce()`      | ❌        | Reduce to single value |
| `reduceRight()` | ❌        | Reduce right-to-left   |


